author: Kruggsmash
description:
Fundraiser Link: https://gofund.me/27ceae3e6

 Welcome to a spooOOooky fundraiser event wherein i'll be playing some spooky games and a whole lot of Dwarf Fortress over the course of 24 hours!

 Honestly fairly undertain of what we'll be playing exatly, but we'll have plenty of time to figure it out, won't we you bearded bastards?

 Proceeds from this stream will go to help our friend in Vietnam who has had an absolutely abysmal year. If you donate any amount and send me an email at kruggsmash@gmail.com i'll do a picture of whatever you want. Dwarf fortressy things are what I do best, but any ol' thing will do. Just note that quality will vary!
title: The 24 Hour Bastar'dween Fundraiser Stream!
